# VoiceRAG Project Overview

This is a RAG (Retrieval-Augmented Generation) application with voice interaction capabilities

## Project Structure

- [app/backend/app.py](mdc:app/backend/app.py) - Main backend application with FastAPI server
- [app/backend/rtmt.py](mdc:app/backend/rtmt.py) - Real-Time Middle Tier for handling OpenAI real-time audio API
- [app/frontend/src/App.tsx](mdc:app/frontend/src/App.tsx) - Main frontend React component
- [app/frontend/src/RagSelector.tsx](mdc:app/frontend/src/RagSelector.tsx) - Component for selecting RAG provider and uploading files

## Key Features

- Voice interface using Azure OpenAI's GPT-4o Realtime API
- RAG with Azure AI Search for answering questions about a knowledge base
- Audio streaming for both input and output
- Support for multiple RAG providers (In-Memory, Llama Index)
- File upload and processing capabilities




